snippet.title: Johnny Depp Abuse: Always Be Recording - Regarding Men #51
snippet.description:
Tom , Paul, and Janice discuss the recent airing of audio tapes that show Amber Heard admitting to having abused Johnny Depp in their relationship.  This makes Depp's previous claims of innocence ring true and shows that she is likely a false accuser.  Always be recording!

https://pjmedia.com/lifestyle/explosive-leaked-confession-of-domestic-abuse-of-johnny-depp-turns-metoo-upside-down/
